{{Expand Italian|Rachele (Michelangelo)|date=December 2011}}
[[File:'Moses' by Michelangelo JBU070.jpg|thumb|''Rachel'']]
The '''''Rachel''''' is a sculpture by [[Michelangelo]] of the [[Old Testament]] figure [[Rachel]]. Like the ''[[Leah (sculpture)|Leah]]'', it was part of the final, 1542-1545 design for the [[tomb of Pope Julius II]] in [[San Pietro in Vincoli]], on which it still remains.

